        "description": "Elite Escape is a puzzle/escape room game where you take on the role of a new recruit for a special forces unit called Alpha-X. As a new joiner, you'll go through a screening process that will assess your analytical and problem-solving skills. This will involve entering a series of rooms where you'll have to analyse various devices around you to figure out a way to progress to the next area. \n\nYou will have to solve a wide variety of puzzles, from logical to numerical and also mechanical which take full advantage of VR hand tracking. Find your way past all those rooms and prove yourself worthy of a place in the world's most elite military unit! \n\n- Challenge yourself and beat 7 puzzle areas \n- Enjoy a wide variety of problems presented in each room \n- Have fun grabbing objects, clicking on buttons and pulling on levers while trying to find your way forward \n- Have a great time solving puzzles in stunning sci-fi environments",
